name: Christiana Peprah
description: I am very active lady, always trying to be fashionable and i do like to smile. I do want to settle down and to create my own family. i like good music, i like to go out sometimes. I like to travel and to meet new people. Hope to travel in the future with my man. I know how to make you smile and feel loved. I want my man to enjoy the atmosphere of love and family, so cozy and warm, and in a private we would share all our love and passion! Do you miss it?
